ĺFrom Phil to Alina, my wife and love of my life.
For memories of lunches and moments shared
in Berkeley Square Mayfair and in
the London Town that we grew to love together
and call our home."Ň
¬As a small boy not far from this very spot, he began running and did not stop
Far across the globe he ran, this beloved, crazy, brilliant man
He loved wine. music and the southern sun, he always gave his best to everyone
He is much missed and that he should, for our south London boy did good
Vincent Hancock 1944-2006"ō
’In celebration of the marriage of
Dan Moss and Claudie Sellers
18th July 2015
So, she leaning on her husband's arm, they turned homeward
by a rosy path which the gracious sun struck out for them in its setting"‚
